Text: Cheers m8 for the up. It was disappointing that 24/7 did not support this fight. Now we'll never hear the end of PBF's verbal jabs as to his high PPV numbers and being the #1P4P boxer. I hope the real boxing fans boycott PBF's PPV, we can just watch it on replay, right? hehe! Thanks again for the up and may PACMAN wins.
Thanks, dude for the up. Proud to be a Filipino !!!
We, here in the island of Cebu, where the PACMAN started his road to boxing greatness, wishes with great fanfare- total success on his campaign today.recanada
